<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>üîê Reset Your Password - {{appName}}</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EF4444 0%, #DC2626 100%);
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EF4444 0%, #DC2626 50%, #B91C1C 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: security-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes security-pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.8; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.05) rotate(180deg); opacity: 1; }
    }
    .security-icon {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .header-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .header-subtitle {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      font-size: 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      background: white;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .security-message {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .reset-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-left: 5px solid #EF4444;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .reset-icon {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EF4444 0%, #DC2626 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }
    .reset-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EF4444 0%, #DC2626 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 18px 36px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .reset-button::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
      transition: left 0.6s;
    }
    .reset-button:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }
    .expiry-notice {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fefce8 0%, #fef3c7 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .expiry-icon {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      margin-right: 15px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .expiry-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #92400e;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .security-tips {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .tips-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0c4a6e;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .tips-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .tips-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #075985;
    }
    .tips-list li::before {
      content: 'üõ°Ô∏è';
      margin-right: 10px;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .alternative-section {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .alternative-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .alternative-link {
      color: #3b82f6;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .footer-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .security-notice {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fecaca 0%, #fca5a5 100%);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
    }
    .security-notice-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #991b1b;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-container { margin: 10px; border-radius: 15px; }
      .header { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .reset-card { padding: 20px; }
      .security-tips { padding: 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="security-icon">
        <svg width="30" height="30" fill="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="header-title">üîê Password Reset</div>
      <div class="header-subtitle">Secure your account with a new password</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="greeting">Hello {{name}}! üëã</div>
      
      <div class="security-message">
        We received a request to reset your password for your {{appName}} account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email. Your account remains secure.
      </div>

      <div class="reset-card">
        <div class="reset-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="white" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
            <path d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #7f1d1d; margin-bottom: 15px;">
          Reset Your Password
        </div>
        <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #991b1b; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          Click the button below to create a new secure password
        </div>
        <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="reset-button">
          üîë Reset Password Now
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="expiry-notice">
        <svg class="expiry-icon" fill="#f59e0b" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="expiry-text">
          <strong>Important:</strong> This reset link expires in 1 hour for your security. After that, you'll need to request a new reset link.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="security-tips">
        <div class="tips-title">
          <svg width="20" height="20" fill="#0c4a6e" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="margin-right: 8px;">
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
          </svg>
          Security Best Practices
        </div>
        <ul class="tips-list">
          <li>Use a unique password that you don't use elsewhere</li>
          <li>Include uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</li>
          <li>Make it at least 12 characters long</li>
          <li>Consider using a password manager</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="alternative-section">
        <div class="alternative-text">
          Can't click the button? Copy and paste this link into your browser:
        </div>
        <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="alternative-link">{{resetUrl}}</a>
      </div>

      <div class="security-notice">
        <div class="security-notice-text">
          üö® If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. Your account is safe and no changes have been made.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-text">
        Your security is our priority. This email was sent from a secure server.
      </div>
      <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 15px;">
        ¬© 2024 {{appName}}. Never share your password or reset links with anyone.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 